data.description: Welcome home to Ave Maria a stunning community in Southwest Florida near the city of Naples Florida. This newer pool home has 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms and a large den/office with over 2300 sqft under air. Plank tile floors throughout, lots of natural light, and an open-concept kitchen with granite countertops. The vaulted ceilings make this home feel spacious and luxurious. Step outside to the enclosed outdoor living space that has a pool overlooking the nature preserve, with a professionally landscaped yard. All the bedroom and bathrooms are spacious with high end finishes, and attention to detail. The mud room off the two-car garage is perfect for rainy days with the pets or setting down packages from the busy day. This home is located close to the town center with shops, restaurants and other great amenities as well as a water park, fitness center, and sports field. This home is vacant and ready for you to call your own.
